OL,3,CTributes to 45-year-old dad killed in
OL,4,CLake District collision
OL,6,FThe family of a 45-year-old father
OL,7,Ffrom Cockermouth, who died following a
OL,8,Ftwo-vehicle collision on the A66, near
OL,9,FThornthwaite, have paid tribute to his
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FCumbria Police say, Pete Faulkner, was
OL,13,Fdriving a car at the time of the
OL,14,Fcollision in the early hours of
OL,15,FSaturday morning.
OL,17,FMr Faulkner had a child, Finn, and
OL,18,Fpartner Hannah who described him as a
OL,19,F"loving and devoted" partner.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
