PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781028676
OL,3,CTributes to 45-year-old dad killed in
OL,4,CLake District collision
OL,6,FHe was the "the kind of person who
OL,7,Fmade the world feel bigger, wider and
OL,8,Fkinder simply by being in it," his
OL,9,Ffamily said.
OL,11,FThe tribute went on to say: "A fell
OL,12,Frunner extraordinaire who came alive
OL,13,Fon the mountains, moving across
OL,14,Fridges, high ground and scree slopes
OL,15,Fcoping with any challenge with grit
OL,16,Fand determination ` especially when
OL,17,Fthere was cake or ice cream at the end.
OL,19,F"He approached every challenge with
OL,20,Fcreativity, tenacity and a great sense
OL,21,Fof humour.
OL,26,@sD@]OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
