PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1781028676
OL,3,CTributes to 45-year-old dad killed in
OL,4,CLake District collision
OL,6,F"He will be missed by many and
OL,7,Fremembered with fondness, gratitude
OL,8,Fand love by all who knew him."
OL,10,FBeing an outdoor lover, his family
OL,11,Frecall him "recreating running shoes
OL,12,Ffrom scratch or shortening a Land
OL,13,FRover so it could climb seemingly
OL,14,Fimpossible steep banks off-road."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, police are continuing to
OL,17,Finvestigate the collision and are
OL,18,Fappealing for any witnesses.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@^O]
